        "text": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "3、来看看世界上最高的网页——"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "block-quote",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "歡迎您訪問世界上最高最長的網頁! 目前這個"
      },
      {
        "text": "網頁高18.94千米",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": "所以滾動這網頁是一種疯狂的娛樂。祝您有很多樂趣。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "→ "
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://worlds-highest-website.com/zh/#pos1",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "查看乐趣"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "divider",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "4、"
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://designscenes.zhubai.love/posts/2155579229599776768#:~:text=%E8%87%AA%E7%95%99%E5%9C%B0%C2%A0%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%EF%BC%8C-,VirtualBuddy,-%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%BE",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "上一期"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "提到 VirtualBuddy 利用了 Mac 虚拟化框架构建。我敬爱的 Mac 大师 Howard Oakley 这次分析了 Apple Silicon Mac 该虚拟化方法的性能。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Mac 提供两个级别（level）的虚拟化支持，一是使用 "
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://developer.apple.com/documentation/hypervisor/apple_silicon",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Hypervisor"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "（VMM）技术的 Parallels、VMware 等商业虚拟机产品，是需要大量代码工作量来填充的中间软件层；二是新的 "
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://developer.apple.com/documentation/virtualization/virtualize_macos_on_a_mac",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Virtualization",
            "bold": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": " 技术，拥有更高的级别，已支持多种关键服务，而且相当轻量化。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "Howard 的测试环境是 macOS 12.5，并且使用 Xcode 14 Beta 编译。绕过复杂的 "
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://eclecticlight.co/2022/07/06/virtualisation-on-apple-silicon-macs-2-how-does-it-work/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "VirtIO 理论"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "，结论为："
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "bulleted-list",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "虚拟机 CPU 的性能与主机（原系统）相似，无法测试 GPU 性能但 Apple 称虚拟机也可用上满血的 Metal 性能；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "写入速度约是主机的 10%，读取速度略高于主机的 50%；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "即使没什么权限限制也无法登录 Apple ID 或 iCloud 服务；"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "总之，Virtualization 提供了出色但有限制的虚拟化性能。Howard 最后也推荐了 "
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://github.com/insidegui/VirtualBuddy",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "VirtualBuddy"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": "。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "→ "
      },
      {
        "type": "link",
        "url": "https://eclecticlight.co/2022/07/04/virtualisation-on-apple-silicon-macs-1-how-well-does-it-work/",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "原文"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "text": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "divider",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": ""
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "5、欧盟的这份元宇宙观察文件《"
      },
      {
        "text": "Metaverse: Opportunities, risks and policy implications",
        "bold": true
      },
      {
        "text": "》现在看显得姗姗来迟。报告不长，里面提到了元宇宙的特征："
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "bulleted-list",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "真实性：人们可以沉浸在虚拟世界中；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "通用性：一个虚拟身份适用于多个设备的多个虚拟平台；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "互通性：不同系统平台间可以无缝交换信息或交互；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "可扩展性：网络架构足够强大，高访问量不会影响用户体验；"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "此外报告也体现出对个人虚拟数据保护的担忧，并谈到了一些政策可能性。经济一节中提到了字节跳动的 Pico 和阿里巴巴的 Nreal 投资。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "结论为，元宇宙既带来了机遇，也带来了风险。因商业竞争、数据保护、责任落实、去中心金融、无障碍等问题尚不清晰，欧盟依然处于观察中。欧盟委员会副主席特别强调了元宇宙对反垄断监管机构带来的新挑战，议会已经开始考虑元宇宙的影响。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "→ "
      },
