  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "誉满解密游戏圈的 Zachtronics 迎来了最后一部作品，在 Last Call BBS 里留下了八款一如既往精致的解谜游戏。虽然是「8合1」，但是每个小游戏都足够玩上一段时间。比如 Dungeons & Diagrams 玩着不顺的话，平均每关都得至少 30-60 分钟，只一个小游戏就得花费数十小时——"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "bulleted-list",
    "children": [
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Sawayama Solitaire：一次性过牌的空当接龙（正常是可以无限翻，间隔为3、2、1）；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Dungeons & Diagrams："
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E6%95%B8%E7%B9%94",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "数织"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "改编的小游戏，有着额外的规则，上头；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "20th Century Food Court：类似 "
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/984800/Automachef/",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Automachef"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " 和"
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/1577620/_The_Signal_State/",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "信号法则"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "，但是 Zach-Like！"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "STEED FORCE Hobby Studio：来拼胶！"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "Kabufuda Solitaire："
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/716500/Eliza/#app_reviews_hash",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Eliza"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " 中的纸牌游戏，同样很靠运气；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "X’BPGH: The Forbidden Path：设定每步 seed（干细胞？）的行为和方向，最终进化到相应有机物，风格很 cult；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "HACK*MATCH："
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/716490/EXAPUNKS/",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "EXAPUNKS"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " 里面的小游戏，只不过也像素化了，并且可以联机；"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list-item",
        "children": [
          {
            "text": "ChipWizard™ Professional："
          },
          {
            "type": "link",
            "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/504210/SHENZHEN_IO/",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "深圳IO"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " Alter 版本，还没细研究；"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "团队解散，不代表创始人 Zach Barth 不再做游戏。在 Kotaku 的采访中提到，Barth 原来是高中微机老师，热爱教学。希望能在其他 side project 里看到 "
      },
      {
        "text": "Zach",
        "italic": true
      },
      {
        "text": " 的影子。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "paragraph",
    "children": [
      {
        "text": "游戏也登录 PC Xbox Game Pass，Steam 也当支持。"
